inline_comments.message:
This is the URL used here: restapi.nearrtric.removeSliceProfile.ransim-mounted=/restconf/config/network-topology:network-topology/topology/topology-netconf/node/{mountName}/yang-ext:mount/ran-network:ran-network/NearRTRIC/{idNearRTRIC}/attributes/sliceProfilesList/{sliceProfileId}


The first replace method, replaces the path variable idNearRTRIC with the actual value and output path is set to tmp.deleteSliceProfileEntry.url

At the later steps, the same URL variable (tmp.deleteSliceProfileEntry.url) is used to replace the other path variable with the values, so that the final URL will have all the path variables replaced.
